---
title: "Ep 183: Superman Returns (15 Year Anniversary!)"
publishDate: "2021-06-23"
category: "major-issues"
episodeNumber: 188
spotifyUrl: "https://comicbookclique.podbean.com/e/ep-183-superman-returns-15-year-anniversary/"
